Class RectangleRn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.garret.perst.RectangleRn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, IValue

    public class RectangleRn
extends java.lang.Object
implements IValue, java.lang.Cloneable
    R-n rectangle class representing n-dimensional wrapping rectangle. This class is used in spatial index.
